Expected: - Got message "Ваш профіль оновлено  Повернутись на початок форуму"              .//a[@href='https://toloka.to/' and contains(text(), 'Повернутись на початок форуму')]
          - After 3-5 sec. message disappeared ???
          - On the profile page, in the "Occupation" text field, appeared entered data     .//span[@class='gen' and contains(text(), 'якийсь текст')]


#3

Summary: Verify that user "Next" button on the "Search" page work properly

Precondition: - User has already created account
              - User is loged into account
              - There are more then one Search list page

Steps: - Open "Search" page (https://toloka.to/featured)
       - Scroll down to the botom of the page
       - Click on the "Next"(Наступна) button              .//a[@href and contains(text(), 'наступна')]

Expected: - Second search list page is opened              .//b[text()='2'] -- перевірка на відсутність атрибута в тесті в Джаві
          - "Previous"(попередня) button uppeared          .//a[@href and contains(text(), 'попередня')]


